channel.title: Kayakings on My New Hugo Site
channel.description: Recent content in Kayakings on My New Hugo Site

item.title: Astronaut Kayaking
item.description: An astronaut took to the lake, In a kayak for leisure’s sweet sake, In zero G style, It floated a while, A space-kayak trip, quite opaque.

item.title: Baker Kayaking
item.description: A baker went out for a row, In a kayak, as waters did flow, With pastries in tote, They managed to float, A sweet, floating bakery to stow.

item.title: Llama Kayaking
item.description: A llama went out for a splash, In a kayak, it made quite a dash, With paddle in hoof, And waterproof roof, It braved through the rapids with flash.

item.title: Turtle Kayaking
item.description: A turtle set off in a kayak, Quite slow, but it never looked back, It paddled with grace, And picked up the pace, A reptilian rowing attack.
